We already have PCC HLD and paper for SC19 and a simple PCC howto: &lt;a href=&quot;https://wiki.whamcloud.com/display/ENG/PCC+Howto+Guide&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://wiki.whamcloud.com/display/ENG/PCC+Howto+Guide&lt;/a&gt;, I think most their content can be reused as the PCC documentation writing.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
